D9518 built by Boulton and Paul Ltd, Norwich
Delivered 3 AAP Norwich; 
Tested 31 May 1918 (right wing low), and 2 June 1918; 
8 AAP Lympne to Orly for US Air Service 3 July 1918, Lt Love; 
Arrived Orly 4 July 1918; 
3rd Aviation Instruction Center Issoudun 21 July 1918 ... 

Aircraft History from The Camel File, Sturtivant and Page, Air-Britain 1993.

